          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/></svg>Real-time flight monitoring &amp; free wait time</li>
            <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/></svg>Curbside or inside meet-and-greet available</li>
