            <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/></svg>Red carpet &amp; umbrella service on request</li>
            <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/></svg>Direct planner coordination &amp; timeline buffers</li>
